title: Stop #7 of 2006/2007 PBRJ Tour - Blue Mountain, Ontario
description: The 7th stop on the 2006/07 Peanut Butter and Rail Jam series went down Saturday, February 3rd at Blue Mountain, Ontario. That's in Canada, that big frozen country with a maple leaf on their flag just north of the United States. Music by: Goons of Doom.
